        description:
          'Take the best parts of out of the capitalist model to fund social good initiatives',
        icon: 'tabler:discount-check',
      },
      {
        title: 'Open Source Projects',
        description:
          'All of our projects are open source and available for anyone to contribute to',
        icon: 'tabler:brand-git',
      },
      {
        title: 'Community Driven',
        description:
          'We allow anyone to participate and contribute to our projects and initiatives',
        icon: 'tabler:building-community',
      },
      {
        title: 'Social Advocacy',
        description:
          'We believe that the best way to make change is to empower people to make change',
        icon: 'tabler:speakerphone',
      },
    ]}
  />

  <!-- Content Widget **************** -->

  <Content
    isReversed
    tagline="Get involved"
    title="Interested in joining?"
    items={[
      {
        title: 'Shared Ownership',
        description:
          'Do you want to work on projects that you are able to share into the success of? We offer shared ownership of all of our projects to our contributors',
      },
      {
        title: 'Multiple Contribution Models',
        description:
          'We offer multiple ways to contribute to our projects, including code, design, and community management',
      },
      {
        title: 'Co-op Model',
        description:
          'The success rate of co-ops is much higher than traditional startups, and we are able to fund our projects through collective collaboration',
      },
    ]}
    image={{
      src: 'https://media.istockphoto.com/id/1208372699/vector/oasis-in-desert.jpg?s=612x612&w=0&k=20&c=YIrJDksxqWjYIKO1YreXo2Sz-ayM4KKCQxba6plg6Ak=',
